props.name: time
props.default: function(): moment.Moment | moment.Duration { return this.duration ? moment.duration('1:0') : moment(); }

props.name: min
props.default: function(): moment.Moment | moment.Duration { return this.duration ? moment.duration('0:0') : moment().hours(0).minutes(0); }

props.name: max
props.default: function(): moment.Moment | moment.Duration { return this.duration ? moment.duration('4:0') : moment().hours(23).minutes(59); }
